<title>逼死华人员工之后，Facebook又把追究死亡真相的清华学霸开除了</title>
<link>http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/aGFDWigQbb</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/aGFDWigQbb</guid>
<description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.3573667711598746&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/RiacFDBX14xBic0V28tbXCwesEibPAw9vaNicQoJwrxRQx1xHSCuq2j4vvStB9Igj9al5jtB8FcoP7uey5cvnNqIQA/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-type=&quot;gif&quot; data-w=&quot;638&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7038007863695938&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCBSe33s2iakdweFGZEM5lGibrLx2pVt0zPL1WbtvXhryvOBtOBwApS6RSPic4MwqxRoGl3UMic0rYeGg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;763&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;那边是NBA总裁拼命在提言论自由&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;这边Facebook就给追求真相的人一个胶带&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;想要真相？&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;闭嘴！开除！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; left=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;前&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;几天，Facebook总部发生的事情想必大家都有所闻，一名38岁的华人软件工程师在总部大楼跳楼自杀，结束了年轻的生命。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; left=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; left=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; left=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;这件事引爆了整个硅谷湾区乃至半个美国的华人群体。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; left=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; left=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; left=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/56tptiaa4SVAeA1Fj4Elqcs8Jfb1fsW5xP1o5iaCF2bWSETEyUKV1CSX5zKtiaXZpSg1dRtPMjXu9WXWFbGicxybZA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;684&quot; helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot; visible=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; left=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;硅谷的华人聚集在Facebook总部外示威，要求Facebook正面回应&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; left=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; left=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;据媒体报道，&lt;span&gt;Qin Chen在南加大攻读CS硕士学位，毕业后更换过两次工作，直到去年入职Facebook，他十分珍惜这次机会。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; left=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; left=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; left=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;到他选择自杀的那一天，他已经在Facebook工作了一年零八个月。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; left=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;但奇怪的是，在Facebook总部的通告中，Qin Chen的死因被曲解为单纯的“去世”&lt;strong&gt;（a passing)&lt;/strong&gt;，至于关于他为什么会产生自杀的想法，Facebook只字未提。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;在&lt;span&gt;Qin Chen去世的第七天，也就是中国人所说的“头七”，魂归，看这世界上最后一眼时，无数湾区工作的华人站了出来。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;431&quot; data-backw=&quot;574&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xAncfn1kzrkySaTPUaYjPCAOWQrAO6IKz9GCFGVtj2&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;</description>
